about.summary: Performs score test using saddlepoint approximation to estimate the null distribution. Also prepares summary statistics for meta-analysis and performs meta-analysis to combine multiple association results. For the latest version, please check <https://github.com/leeshawn/SPAtest>.

name: r-spatest
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '3.0.2' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-spatest
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/SPAtest_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/SPAtest/SPAtest_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7a5e02f636df4c299d3a2d36033f26492b6db51f04a5cd1c2ff17e7ec1a4e831

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('SPAtest')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('SPAtest')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=SPAtest
  license: GPL-2
  summary: Performs score test using saddlepoint approximation to estimate the null distribution.
    Also prepares summary statistics for meta-analysis and performs meta-analysis to
    combine multiple association results. For the latest version, please check <https://github.com/leeshawn/SPAtest>.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - endrebak

# Package: SPAtest
# Type: Package
# Title: Score Test and Meta-Analysis Based on Saddlepoint Approximation
# Version: 3.0.2
# Date: 2020-01-09
# Author: Rounak Dey, Seunggeun Lee
# Maintainer: Rounak Dey <deyrnk@umich.edu>
# Description: Performs score test using saddlepoint approximation to estimate the null distribution. Also prepares summary statistics for meta-analysis and performs meta-analysis to combine multiple association results. For the latest version, please check <https://github.com/leeshawn/SPAtest>.
# Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
# License: GPL (>= 2)
# Repository: CRAN
# NeedsCompilation: no
# Packaged: 2020-01-10 05:03:21 UTC; Rounak
# Date/Publication: 2020-01-10 13:50:03 UTC
smithy_version:
No azure token. Create a token and
put it in ~/.conda-smithy/azure.token
3.7.0
